race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: LEONI BALE (1) has a strong record here with six wins and four placings from 17 starts. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.36) in a Grade 5, finishing a 10 length fourth. Appeals as a leading chance in this. JOLLY OLLIE (4) hit the frame latest (25.83) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has already won three times from this draw. Looks a key chance on best figures. LAGNICOURT (3) broke a string of placings finishing in the money three on end before a last start fourth (25.49) at Maitland. Great chance to atone. LONE SHARK (8) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.
